### 10) Users - list
GET http://localhost:4000/api/users

---

### 11) Create user (POST JSON)
POST http://localhost:4000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Prueba",
  "username": "prueba",
  "password": "secret",
  "role": "user"
}

---
### 12) Upload audio (FIXED multipart)
POST http://localhost:4000/api/upload-audio
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

audio: @archivo.wav
latitude: -33.456789
longitude: -70.123456
id_user: 1
model: Samsung A54
os_version: Android 14